rows.label: qev035103_MSG0001
rows.name: Zarch here. Have you sighted Odsent?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035103_MSG0003
rows.name: I will head out at once. Keep him there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035103_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask how, exactly, you're supposed to "keep him there."

rows.label: qev035103_MSG0004
rows.name:
You cannot control beast's mind like Prone.
So you must beat beast unconscious![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035103_MSG0005
rows.name: That also makes retraining easier for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev035103_MSG0006
rows.name:
Yes, warrior! Beat beast unconscious!
This also makes retraining easier for me.[ST:wait ]
